<h2 id="csim-master-2016-2017">CSIM Master, 2016-2017</h2>

<p>You will find on this page all the material related to the Real-Time Interaction course.</p>

<h3 id="general-information-about-the-course">General information about the course</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/18Dwo_TU-fEMYThNJh4NZCLkp7n9jb58RV_UXWCb95DI/edit?usp=sharing">Course presentation document</a></li>
